title: Verity

message: >
  If you use Verity in your research, please cite this software.

type: software

authors:
  - family-names: Hoke
    given-names: Cole

repository-code: https://github.com/cole-h06/Verity

url: https://github.com/cole-h06/Verity

license: MIT

abstract: >
  Verity is a graph-based credibility inference engine for information
  networks. It models sources and claims as a bipartite graph to infer
  the credibility of every source and claim.
